{"tid":815280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【海航財困】賣資產後用唔著！傳海航棄租中環寫字樓","createTime":"2018-09-12T02:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T09:59:46.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"74fa58778b989e1741ee37bd528082428abe66e7","tid":815280,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T02:46:20.000Z","msg":"【海航財困】賣資產後用唔著！傳海航棄租中環寫字樓<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180912/58671395\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180912%2F58671395&d=%2Fw%2Buz7xwB5ubYUDeAToF1NtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=06bca633\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180912%2F58671395&h=f06b6810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180912/58671395</a><br />\n<br />\n《彭博》引述消息人士透露，海航將放棄租用中環合共8層寫字空間，雖然報道未有指明地點，但則同時引述消息人士透露，中環交易廣場三座部份樓層正在招租。<br />\n<br />\n根據土地註冊處資料，海航於今年三月份簽訂一份為期九年的租約，而這個租約業主是置地，並於6月份起租。但報道引述消息指，海航從未有搬入有關寫字樓，亦未有進行裝修。"},{"pid":"dc6c9c256b1cd361e874247cd82b23cb9da31d60","tid":815280,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T02:50:01.000Z","msg":"撻訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09a87c359b39658b683703e7d494cb4af49059d","tid":815280,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T02:50:40.000Z","msg":"美國D資產開始俾人凍結，叫人印多D銀紙再搵老王特批出境咪有錢係香港再掃貨囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811d2c024d7aa7b5b1aeb442a8db103989c5af17","tid":815280,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T02:57:12.000Z","msg":"慘豬豬, 簽咗約後連裝修錢都冇, 拖咗半年就要退租, 仲要輸死約期租金<br />\n<br />\n早幾年D中資大行一窩蜂咁去中上環搶租寫字樓, 而家強国興玩逆周期因子, 今次會唔會係一窩蜂咁租都唔交走佬呢?"},{"pid":"66ce01747d6f03e3aea3fba283122bf78b445c51","tid":815280,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:15:48.000Z","msg":"寫字空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc7b1c8d75e1d37037ac9a041d1439925db1fe38","tid":815280,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02fb8fff2cc29e1a5a0e6a18f6b48a85370d4cd","tid":815280,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:59:46.000Z","msg":"租紅磡"}]}